title: (x) "this is like 7 dog gifts" connected geometric script - Ribjoint {Claes}
content:
Please help me identify this script. I'm stumped!

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20141114135903im_/http:/typophile.com/files/script2_5232.jpg)
author: aimzter

comments.content: Don't know it, but you might consider [Memima](http://web.archive.org/web/20141114135903/http:/www.fontshop.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=catalog.fontpackage&startrow=1&records=&currpage=1&totalrecords=4&displayfontid=TO.10008.0.0&fontRendererText=like+7+dog+gifts) an improvement.

'Kulukundis' may be an alternate as well.

Dav

YES! that's it. Ribjoint.  
Thank you for all your help everyone!
